locality: 14½ km on Babati rd from Makiungu jct, then left to powerline, then 1½ km up the line. Rolling hills with a rich low woodland-bushland 3-5(-9)m: Brachystegia spiciformis, Combretum spp, Catunaregam, many other woody & herbaceous species.
Mgori Forest Reserve, Nduamughanga Village Forest Reserve
9 km along rd from Makiungu to Misughaa, then 1½ km along new rd to Mnane. Escarpment slopes, coarse mosaic of miombo woodland & clearings, Brachystegia microphylla 15-20m the dominant.
T5. 2 -3 miles on Kibakwe to Motta track.
Mgori Forest Reserve; Duamughanga Village Forest reserve; Miombo Bushland with bushy patches.

Entre Nangade e Palma, aos 16 km de Nangade.
